Tusk*It is a program which allows to combine a popular issue tracking system 
(like Trac or Bugzilla) with Agile/Extreme Programming methodologies.


CREDITS

Developers: Dmitry Mozzherin, Javier Castro Barba, Janos Hajagos

Inspirations: Peter Armstrong and his 'Flexible Rails' book (http://flexiblerails.com/)

Icons by: Mark James (http://www.famfamfam.com/lab/icons/silk/)


 

